{
  "texts": [
    "Experiments on a public dataset from ASSISTments, which contained student's math assignments and classwork, demonstrated the efficacy and viability of the proposed method.",
    "The accuracy of the MFA-DKT model reached up to 98%.",
    "Most academic institution's learning management systems (LMSs) provide access to a wealth of data on student activities.",
    "Prior studies on predictive analytics employing LMS activity data, however, did not sufficiently account for student behaviors as time series.",
    "LSTM networks proposed in the study by Chen and Cui (2020) to assess the temporal behaviors of students by using their data on LMS for early course success prediction."
  ]
}